Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.01,0:00:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我必須要做才行
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.00,0:00:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這大概是夢一般的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.54,0:00:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家夢想中的科學解決一切的和平時代
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.89,0:01:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,基本上所有的車和摩托 以及工廠所使用的能源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.98,0:01:04.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都可以從天空中獲取
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.13,0:01:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了資源而產生的爭端也完全消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.66,0:01:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些全都是5年前所開發的示現引擎的功勞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.02,0:01:20.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示現引擎被建立在相模灘中心的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.08,0:01:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人工島 Blue Island上
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.16,0:01:27.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從那裡利用宇宙衛星向全世界傳送能源
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.16,0:01:42.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早的狀態也很好啊 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.67,0:01:44.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好 鈴木婆婆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.79,0:01:48.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也能清楚地看到引擎先生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.42,0:01:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該會是一個好的天氣
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.18,0:01:50.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.91,0:01:55.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發明那座引擎的其實是我的爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.92,0:02:04.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是爺爺的發明品
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界上唯一一輛能飛的摩托
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.27,0:02:10.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我叫它汪汪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.38,0:02:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人家們都說 現在是個很好的時代
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.45,0:02:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也覺得是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.07,0:02:24.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 我非常喜歡現在這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.38,0:02:27.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常喜歡這座島和島上的人們
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.35,0:02:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天下午就會到達Blue Island
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.48,0:02:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我就很期待見到你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:38.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我哦 葵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.29,0:02:44.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 飯做好了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.37,0:02:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.90,0:00:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,title
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:19.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,532)}FIRST OPERATION
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 幫我端一下味增湯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.21,0:03:43.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 加了秋葵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.84,0:03:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今早在院子裡摘的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.81,0:03:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,秋葵 秋葵 秋…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.45,0:03:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.62,0:04:02.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 去叫爺爺來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.79,0:04:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.07,0:04:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺 一色健次郎博士
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.43,0:04:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃飯了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.54,0:04:26.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰打擾我研究
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.88,0:04:28.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爺爺的孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.13,0:04:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你確實是我的孫女 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:36.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經8小時57分12秒不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.36,0:04:38.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 能再次見到你太讓我高興了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也是 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊抱！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.93,0:04:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…你們每天早上都要來一次才滿意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.79,0:04:49.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.50,0:04:56.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 葵要回來了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天回來哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.07,0:05:06.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放學後我就會去接她
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.88,0:05:08.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃也會來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.59,0:05:12.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 今天商店有限時特價
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.23,0:05:15.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一盒子雞蛋只要10日元！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.35,0:05:16.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不能放過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.88,0:05:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 也就是說不來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.98,0:05:21.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就為了區區一盒雞蛋 真是小氣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.33,0:05:25.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道我們家這麼窮都是誰害的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.52,0:05:33.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 這是…研究一定要用的東西…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:37.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,色譜解析裝置是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做什麼用的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.13,0:05:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以 姐姐一個人去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.04,0:05:52.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這是電車費
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,錢能撐到去看望媽媽那個時候嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.31,0:05:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.55,0:06:01.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是如果不快點吃完的話 會遲到的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.91,0:06:04.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 已經這個時間了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.21,0:06:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們出門了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.97,0:06:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.32,0:06:12.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.49,0:06:41.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須盡快完成
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.06,0:06:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是Pingu02 呼叫司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.57,0:06:55.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,目前高度29000
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是司令部 開始引導
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.17,0:07:03.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(654,570)\fad(350,0)}Blue Island聯合防衛軍司令部
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.77,0:07:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請上升到方位030 高度35000米凖
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.82,0:07:04.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.52,0:07:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美軍也發現了目標
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.63,0:07:12.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,周邊各國否認牽涉其中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.45,0:07:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接觸了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.32,0:07:27.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全機均被擊毀
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未確認部隊從雷達上消失
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.61,0:07:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.20,0:07:35.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發動特級警戒態勢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連接艦隊 以此為最優先事項
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.02,0:07:42.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 下一節體育課是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,中小學各班一起在操場上進行躲避球遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.20,0:07:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了 下一次我一定會贏
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.40,0:07:52.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 一色
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.43,0:07:53.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.49,0:07:56.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 葵她…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:08:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 雖然出席數有些慘不忍睹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:02.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是考慮到她有病在身 而且也完成了自己的課題
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.23,0:08:07.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,權衡這些因素 你們可以一起升學
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.60,0:08:10.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.54,0:08:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點告訴桃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.69,0:08:16.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:18.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 小葉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.12,0:08:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,優 優君出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.82,0:08:29.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧 太危險了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.41,0:08:30.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還差一點
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.50,0:08:39.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.73,0:08:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很危險哦 為什麼要爬到那種地方
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.01,0:08:48.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為這傢伙從巢裡掉出來掛到了樹枝上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.61,0:08:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥好可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.31,0:08:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 交給我好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜姐姐…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.76,0:09:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 茜姐姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.98,0:09:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 一色？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.49,0:09:25.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.41,0:09:33.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.00,0:09:38.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明知道自己恐高的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.69,0:09:40.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.72,0:09:45.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我非常喜歡姐姐這一點 但還是很擔心哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.30,0:09:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 桃
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.41,0:10:00.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓你們久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.43,0:10:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了我一個人而讓你們準備直升機 真是抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.26,0:10:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我迫不及待地想回到島上
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.88,0:10:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請交給我們吧 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.06,0:10:16.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這架最新式的傾轉旋翼機搭載有
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.12,0:10:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能利用Blue Island所傳送能源的Energy Rain System
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.88,0:10:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保證會讓你享受到舒適的空中旅行
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.75,0:10:33.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.30,0:10:37.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬上就能見面了 等我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.47,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 葵已經坐上飛往這裡的飛機了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.97,0:10:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 我們也要趕快
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.16,0:10:49.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.32,0:10:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見了 各位
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.90,0:10:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:18.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.66,0:11:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 你的意思是 敵人的目標是這裡嗎 總理
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:46.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(646,572)}Blue Island 管理局局長室
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.18,0:11:39.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 應該是恐怖分子或者是某個國家
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.62,0:11:43.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了示現引擎而發動的侵略
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.73,0:11:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說 一定是人類的作為了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:49.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外還能是什麼呢？局長
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.02,0:11:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道你想說 那東西是那個男人所說的「Alone」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.15,0:11:57.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會啟動對策
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.89,0:12:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果情況發生了變化 請再次聯繫我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然7年前 沒有一個人願意傾聽
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.25,0:12:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此你被迫承擔起事故責任而遭到驅逐 然而
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:15.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許你是正確的 一色博士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.24,0:12:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的「Alone」 果然來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.83,0:12:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是這一次不會讓你們得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.69,0:12:34.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們家那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.23,0:12:35.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.49,0:12:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.42,0:12:48.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧 爺爺？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.36,0:12:50.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.56,0:12:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有呼吸
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.03,0:12:57.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不是真的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.29,0:12:59.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺！爺爺！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.29,0:13:06.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.74,0:13:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.03,0:13:08.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.89,0:13:10.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 還以為會死掉呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:18.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我送給爺爺的布偶？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.60,0:13:19.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說話了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.23,0:13:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.82,0:13:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是毛啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.91,0:13:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示現回路的封裝雖然成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.40,0:13:37.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但還是沒能全部抵消位相轉移的衝擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.47,0:13:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是意識被彈出了體外啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.21,0:13:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說並沒有死是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.80,0:13:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.68,0:13:48.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 現在這種事怎樣都好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.70,0:13:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好你妹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.63,0:13:52.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌 我的孫女
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.54,0:13:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去的方法 總有一天會找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.22,0:13:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比起這事…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.73,0:13:59.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我終於完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.74,0:14:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成是指？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.97,0:14:01.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.23,0:14:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這 是那兒！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.84,0:14:12.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.05,0:14:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我嘔心瀝血半輩子的研究的結晶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.26,0:14:17.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某種意義上來說 示現引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.82,0:14:20.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不過是研製它的過程中所誕生的副產品
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.30,0:14:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鑰匙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.30,0:14:26.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜 這是只有你才能使用的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.58,0:14:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿著吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:29.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有我？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.85,0:14:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.76,0:14:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}東京都新大島特別行政區通知
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:49.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}新大島及伊豆大島群島 進入特別警戒狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.80,0:14:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道三原山…？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.19,0:14:50.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}註：位於伊豆大島上的活火山
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不是火山噴發
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.73,0:14:56.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最嚴重的災難將會發生在Blue Island上
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.77,0:14:58.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Island上？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:14:59.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.27,0:15:11.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 總之先把本體裝進這裡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.64,0:15:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰 冰箱？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.41,0:15:17.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,桃 你去地下避難
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.27,0:15:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算是掩體炸彈也沒辦法摧毀這個
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:23.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們家的事 就拜託了 桃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.47,0:15:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們已經約定過了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.10,0:15:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在媽媽出院前 我們倆會好好保護這裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.63,0:15:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.00,0:15:32.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 爺爺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.82,0:15:33.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.87,0:15:36.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Blue Island居民已經避難完成
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,允許使用導彈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.99,0:15:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.69,0:15:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各機 火力保險裝置解除 敵人馬上就進入視野了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.12,0:15:49.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那就是敵人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.12,0:15:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了 散開！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.54,0:15:54.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光束武器？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.71,0:16:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被浪打到就麻煩了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.45,0:16:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將高度升到極限
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.14,0:16:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.48,0:16:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有東西在發光
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.77,0:16:14.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是防衛軍在攻擊Alone吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:15.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.98,0:16:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「Alone」？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.10,0:16:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7年前 國立能源研究所
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.85,0:16:23.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示現引擎實驗號機
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.84,0:16:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,控制樓內
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.33,0:16:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,代碼104發生
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.44,0:16:27.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,研究樓設備遭到嚴重損壞
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.69,0:16:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現已陷入失控狀態
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.15,0:16:33.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽 好高啊 好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:35.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能往下看哦 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.25,0:16:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 一定會得救的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.84,0:16:47.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白 我現在就過去 堅持住
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:53.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那 那是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.01,0:17:04.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真白！茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.05,0:17:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙的目標是示現引擎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:10.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,示現引擎？為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.22,0:17:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道 但是引擎如果被破壞的話 世界就完蛋了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.29,0:17:16.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓緊吧 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.23,0:17:17.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.25,0:17:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,護衛艦被幹掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.69,0:17:38.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.45,0:17:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來 天城中尉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.36,0:17:41.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.76,0:17:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民間機？為什麼會在這種地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.77,0:18:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,民間機 立即離開這片空域！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.53,0:18:07.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 無法控制了！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.02,0:18:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過分…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.81,0:18:21.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！葵乘在上面！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.05,0:18:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕了 茜
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.58,0:18:25.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣子會撞在引擎上的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.21,0:18:31.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.11,0:18:37.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直前進的話 會有通往頂層的升降機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.28,0:18:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.03,0:18:58.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備緊急著陸！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.67,0:18:59.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.89,0:19:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大小姐 請做好衝擊準備
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.50,0:19:11.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 快點！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:18.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.88,0:19:26.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.88,0:19:30.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.34,0:19:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.78,0:19:37.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.77,0:19:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好高啊 好怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.30,0:19:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:19:59.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.01,0:20:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:05.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.60,0:20:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別過來…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.03,0:20:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:38.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.59,0:20:44.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葵！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.11,0:20:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.56,0:21:41.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,茜 我們在飛哦！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.01,0:21:43.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的 為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.53,0:21:46.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對了 茜不是怕高嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.54,0:21:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事的 已經不怕了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.65,0:21:52.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Operation成功了！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.79,0:21:56.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的究極發明Vivid System的力量！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.08,0:21:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Vivid System？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.11,0:22:05.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.83,0:22:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵人突破第二警戒線
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.76,0:22:10.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去會登陸的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.00,0:22:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,城市…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.30,0:22:21.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想拯救城市嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.01,0:22:24.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們擁有這種力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.40,0:22:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個世界上唯一能夠對抗Alone的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.77,0:22:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.73,0:22:33.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.35,0:22:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.09,0:22:36.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們兩個仔細聽好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.22,0:22:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合體吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.58,0:22:40.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,合體？
Comment: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ED
Comment: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,preview
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.16,0:24:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初次見面 我是二葉葵
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.69,0:24:18.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然出現的敵人Alone
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.10,0:24:21.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很可怕 但是如果和茜一起的話就能戰鬥！
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.16,0:24:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,次回 重疊的瞬間
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.62,0:24:26.74,*Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要保護大家

Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:48.84,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}途切れない気持ちが私の道標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:51.68,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}しゃがみ込んだここから
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:23:00.26,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}続く明日へと行こう 君と
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.47,0:23:05.83,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}読めない風向きに 何度も迷うけど
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:11.56,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いつもイメージ通りって たぶんつまんない
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:17.16,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}ありふれて見えても 泣き笑いの日々で
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.48,0:23:26.53,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}地図をはみ出しそうな想いが溢れて…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:34.92,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}全部が繋がるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.23,0:23:42.69,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今日だって最高の未来に変わってく
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.99,0:23:48.48,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}昨日の涙さえ誇れる場所になるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.73,0:23:54.81,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}分け合った痛みを 語り合ったその夢を
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:24:08.13,OP_Theme_ep01,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}いま両手で抱き締めよう もっと君と

Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.52,0:22:48.84,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}永恆的心情是我的路標
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.09,0:22:51.68,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}從屈膝在地的這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.98,0:23:00.26,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}走向相連的明天 與你一同
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.47,0:23:05.83,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}難以解讀的風向 無數次令我迷茫
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.11,0:23:11.56,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}然而總在意料之中 或許也會頗為無趣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.81,0:23:17.16,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}眼看之下平凡無奇 洋溢歡笑與淚水的日子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.48,0:23:26.53,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}充滿了幾乎讓地圖 難以承載的情感
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.55,0:23:34.92,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}一切都彼此相通
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.23,0:23:42.69,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}今天也將化為最為美好的未來
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.99,0:23:48.48,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}就連昨天的淚水也將轉變為驕傲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.73,0:23:54.81,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}一起承擔的苦痛 共同分享的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.08,0:24:08.13,OP_Theme_ep01_ch,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,300)\blur3}此刻 用雙手緊抱在懷中 與你更加親密